description: Travis Thorpe is a 3rd degree Triskellion Wiccan Priest, High Priest of the Temple of Adrastos, A Paranormal Investigator, A former infantryman in the US Army, a former police officer, and a behavior detection instructor.  Travis has taken the road less traveled when it comes to tackling the laws of the paranormal, and is with us today to tell us about his fascinating journey and theories...
